# Coloring in zathura

## Search result highlight
### Can use either hex code or rgba surround by double quotes

set highlight-color "rgba(69, 133, 256, 0.3)" #bright blue
set highlight-active-color "rgba(69, 133, 256, 0.8)"


## Status bar (at the bottom)
set statusbar-bg "#282828"
set statusbar-fg "#ebdbb2"


## Input bar (for example when searching)
set inputbar-bg "#282828"
set inputbar-fg "#ebdbb2"


## Define colors to use in "recolor"
set recolor-lightcolor "#282828"
set recolor-darkcolor "#ebdbb2"


set recolor-keephue "true"

# Sets "recolor" palette as default
set recolor true
